    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1889-10-28T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1889-10-28T00:00:00-05:00" n="18" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d18">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Blaine</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Grant</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1889-10-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">October</hi> 28,
                            1889</date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 29.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Your dispatch (No. 37) of the 10th instant
                        relative to the alleged illegal arrest and imprisonment of Mr. Frank Xavier
                        Fisher has been received.</p>
                <p>Your note to the foreign office in regard to the case is approved as in
                        accordance with the Department’s instructions.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">James G. Blaine.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
